==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: starchy
<hw>starch"y</hw> <pr>(-⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Of
or pertaining to starch.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Containing or consisting of starch; -- used
especially of foods.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Resembling starch; stiff.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>4.</sn> <def>Stiffened by use of starch; starched{1}; -- of
clothing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>5.</sn> <def>Formal in manner; precise.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> starch.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Starcraft</ent>⟦br⟧
